1 3. Shall not be located within one hundred (100) feet from any
2 public road right-of-way.
3 4. Shall not be located within one and one-half (1 1/2) miles
4 from the centerline of any airport, public school, or hospital.
5 5. Shall not be located within two (2) miles from a wildlife
6 refuge, wildlife management area, or any body of water used by
7 migratory waterfowl.
8 SECTION 2. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
9 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
10 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
11 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
